{"tid":2203417,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【美國大選】司法部長批中國威脅大過俄羅斯 民主黨人斥說謊","createTime":"2020-09-15T10:06:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T11:44:09.000Z","uid":70063,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2d8be7d905736e4da122120ebed49bd583020526","tid":2203417,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T10:06:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200907/UC3NU6THXBDU3PS2YHEWZWEHOM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200907%2FUC3NU6THXBDU3PS2YHEWZWEHOM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuTHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=d30dd35f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200907%2FUC3NU6THXBDU3PS2YHEWZWEHOM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=6a499ea8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200907/UC3NU6THXBDU3PS2YHEWZWEHOM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n美國司法部長巴爾（William Barr）上周三指，在11月的總統大選中中國的威脅比俄羅斯大，民主黨的眾議院情報委員會主席希夫（Adam Schiff）指他說謊、誤導美國人。<br />\n<br />\n在去年獲得總統特朗普提名出任司法部長的巴爾，上周三向美國有線新聞網絡（CNN）表示就干擾美國大選方面，中國的威脅比起俄羅斯大，「我看過情報，這是我可以下的結論」，但他沒有透露更多細節。<br />\n<br />\n希夫周日指巴爾的言論「是司法部長的虛假陳述」、「誤導美國人」，問及他是否認為巴爾說謊，希夫說︰「他基本上就是這樣做，我不想這樣說，但現實是這樣。」他又補充，「明顯地巴爾已準備做任何事或發表任何言論力撐特朗普」。<br />\n<br />\n競選總統的民主黨候選人拜登在上周五也曾表示，不認同中國是對選舉最大的威脅。不過報道引述情報指，有報告反映將會有黑客攻擊，影響11月3日的大選。在上屆大選中，美國情報人員發現俄羅斯曾發動一場網絡攻擊，干擾有利特朗普選情。國家反間諜與安全中心主管伊萬拿（William Evanina）上月曾表示，俄羅斯、中國和伊朗都會有行動干擾大選，認為俄羅斯會追擊拜登，而中國則不希望特朗普勝選連任。"},{"pid":"e3bc800e3fca323501af13f415d95b07671b551c","tid":2203417,"uid":127575,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T10:08:08.000Z","msg":"民主黨賣美國係常識"},{"pid":"679ce581382ec7f3f0ae54c9b23aad9773f99ac3","tid":2203417,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T10:08:56.000Z","msg":"以我記得美國人通常好尊重司法部長？"},{"pid":"af5e50bb50290add7f67a1c3768ad10c3ac8f940","tid":2203417,"uid":52194,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T10:10:29.000Z","msg":"呢樣真<br />\n俄仔要搞你直接岀兵吞<br />\n係支那又要認屎認屁玩陰招<br />\n你睇聯合國已經比佢廢緊"},{"pid":"fb8eb8c2cb72736914626319a3f7b7a20452f78c","tid":2203417,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"679ce581382ec7f3f0ae54c9b23aad9773f99ac3","tid":2203417,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T10:08:56.000Z","msg":"以我記得美國人通常好尊重司法部長？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T10:17:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />司法部長=律政司<br />\n唔係法官"},{"pid":"11cd6c49f14725390df4027a2286d1a9bd32a00b","tid":2203417,"uid":60366,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T10:20:46.000Z","msg":"咁就大選嚟講嘅話應該係俄國問題大啲嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他方面就未必係"},{"pid":"cee35b28770682d9610f96a3fabf6a42bd21e9b1","tid":2203417,"uid":44513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"af5e50bb50290add7f67a1c3768ad10c3ac8f940","tid":2203417,"uid":52194,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T10:10:29.000Z","msg":"呢樣真<br />\n俄仔要搞你直接岀兵吞<br />\n係支那又要認屎認屁玩陰招<br />\n你睇聯合國已經比佢廢緊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T10:21:12.000Z","msg":"同埋俄國根本無力也無心取代美國的地位同秩序"},{"pid":"4f40f478e5721d653f60f7f6110edab5d9138041","tid":2203417,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cee35b28770682d9610f96a3fabf6a42bd21e9b1","tid":2203417,"uid":44513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"af5e50bb50290add7f67a1c3768ad10c3ac8f940","tid":2203417,"uid":52